    "reviews": [
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2021-07",
        "text": "Iva Dostal is hands down the most amazing wedding photographer. When I got engaged, the first thing I did was begin the search for someone who could truly capture the beauty and authenticity of our wedding day. I also wanted someone who is structured and organized.\nIva was the PERFECT find. She met with us 2 times before the wedding and created an easy to follow timeline.\nShe walked us through poses and truly captured the most special moments. Our wedding and reception were outdoors and she ran all over making sure to get the best shots!\nI would 100% recommend Iva!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2019-10",
        "text": "Iva was amazing - hire her for your wedding! You won't regret it. She has a fantastic eye and the quality of her photos is excellent. We are so thrilled with the variety and quantity of photos we have, and everyone we've shown them to has gasped at their beauty (literally). Iva was great to work with, her communication was on point, and we really enjoyed her presence on the day of our wedding. We can't recommend her enough!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2020-02",
        "text": "Iva was a pleasure to work with and we couldn't have asked for a better wedding photographer.  The pictures turned out beautifully and she captured the spirit of the wedding.  Iva was very flexible when it came to meeting our schedule, timely in all our correspondence, and very organized and professional on the big day."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2018-07",
        "text": "Iva photographed our wedding and was so incredibly wonderful to work with from beginning to end.  She created a fun atmosphere for taking pictures and was very personable and easy to work with.  She surveyed the venue prior to the wedding day to get a feel for the venue and where the best shots could take place.  Her attention to detail is evident in her work. We could not be more pleased with her beautiful pictures - they captured our day perfectly.  Thank you so much, Iva!  Mike and Holly."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2021-10",
        "text": "Iva photographed our wedding in August in Granby, CO, she was exceptional. She hung with us through the pandemic and a date change. She met with us before the wedding and helped us find the perfect places for shots. The pictures are beautiful and she really went above and beyond in customer service and talent."
      }
    ]
  },
